@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title Stake delegation and vote delegation are independent

[Your stake credential\n(part of your address)] as SC

package "Stake delegation" {
  [Stake pool\n(block production + rewards)] as POOL
}

package "Vote delegation" {
  [A specific DRep] as DREP
  [Abstain (built-in)] as AB
  [No Confidence (built-in)] as NC
}

SC --> POOL : delegate stake
SC --> DREP : delegate vote
SC ..> AB : or
SC ..> NC : or

note bottom of SC
  You can stake to one pool and vote-delegate
  to a different DRep, and change either without
  touching the other. In the Conway era, rewards
  accrue but can only be withdrawn once the stake
  credential has delegated its vote.
end note
@enduml
